<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The [[Image:FreeGridWorkbench.svg|24px]] '''FreeGrid Workbench''' is an [[External_workbenches|external workbench]] for generating FreeGrid storage system components. In which are included grids, boxes and bit cartridge holders.
</div>

[[Image:FreeGrid_example.png|500px]]

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
{{Caption|Example of a FreeGrid 6x4 grid containing 3 boxes and one bit cartridge holder.}}
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Installation ==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# Install the FreeGrid Workbench via the [[Image:AddonManager.svg|24px]] [[Std_AddonMgr|Addon Manager]]. For manual installation, see [[Installing_more_workbenches|Installing more workbenches]].
# Restart FreeCAD.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Tools ==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* Create a storage box
* Create a bit cartridge holder
* Create a storage grid
* Generate inner box profile
</div>

